# Pawtoberfest Update – A New Animal Era Begins! 🐾
Oktoberfest just got a whole lot cuter – pets are here! Meet Briny, Teddy, and Pomkin: three lovable companions ready to bond, grow, and explore Oktoberfest with you. Feed them, train them, pet them, and help them evolve through our brand-new care system.

[media]

[media]

[media]

**What’s New in Pawtoberfest?**


🐱 New Pets – Unique personalities, adorable animations & color rarities (common to epic)

📊 Care System – Manage happiness, hunger, stamina & XP to help your pet thrive

🎮 Pet Trial – Try a pet for free! Keep it by leveling to 5 or buy it at a reduced price

🛍️ Pet Shop – Adopt more pets with Pet Shards and grow your animal collection

👕 Pet-Inspired Outfits – Match your look to your new best friend in cozy, themed styles

**Plus all your Oktoberfest favorites:**

🎯 Classic Fairground Games

🎢 Thrilling Rides

👗 Avatar Customization

🎤 Social Fun & Mini-Games

Whether you’re bonding with Briny or dressing like Teddy, Pawtoberfest is your cutest Oktoberfest yet! 🧡🐾
